'''Ruben Delgaug''' was an [[artist]].

He was a master artist, a painter, who was long dead by the 1360s [[DR]].

Among his works was a set of four paintings of [[Waterdeep]] during each season, sized 8×10 inches (20×25 centimeters). These were rare and priced at 200 [[gp]] each, and 1600 gp for a full set. A set of these paintings was present at the [[Vipers' Nest]] [[bandit]] hideout in [[1369 DR]].{{Cite dungeon/75/Into the Nest of Vipers|66}}
